  <insidersGuide><![CDATA[<p style="font-size: 18px; font-weight: bold; text-align: center;">Good to know</p>
<p><strong>Hiking trails: </strong>The Portofino National Park</p>
<p><strong>Terrain: </strong>Narrow mountain side paths</p>
<p><strong>Best time to go: </strong>April - May &amp; September - October. Visiting around the edge of the season will mean the climate is a bit cooler and the towns won't be as busy</p>
<p><strong>Recommended for: </strong>Intermediate hikers</p>
<p><strong>Fly into: </strong>Genoa (approx. 2 hours)</p>
<p><strong>Transfer time: </strong>approx. 45 mins from Genoa airport or 1 hour 30 mins from Pisa airport by private car</p>]]></insidersGuide>
